    "description": {
      "zh": "汽油内燃机使用的火花塞。点燃油气混合物的火花，是由数千或数万伏电压在电极间放电产生的，火花塞会在发动机每个运行周期的做功冲程中点火。",
      "en": "Spark plugs are used for gasoline internal combustion engines. Ignition of the fuel-air mixture is produced by electric discharge with a voltage of several thousand or tens of thousands of volts, emerging between the electrodes. The plug fires on each round, at one point of the engine operating cycle."
